Item.name: Acquisition payment

Item.description: Permanent, readable form of data, information, or knowledge related to acquisition.

Item.name: Project infrastructure

Item.name: Project infrastructure needs
Item.description: Identified infrastructure needs of the project.

Item.name: Project lessons learned

Item.description: [6.4.13.1] The purpose of the maintenance process is to sustain the capability of the system to provide a service.

Product, and to properly attend to intended critical disposal needs.
